Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}, doxyparse, libgetopt-euclid-perl, libgraph-perl, liblist-compare-perl, libtest-class-perl, libtest-exception-perl, libyaml-perl, libclass-accessor-perl, libstatistics-descriptive-perl, libstatistics-online-perl
Recommends: graphviz
Description: multi-language source code analysis toolkit
 Analizo parses source code in multiple languages and report useful information
 about it, such as module dependency, source code metrics and more.
 .
 Analizoi uses doxyparse to parse the source code, and is currently tested and
 expected to work well with C, C++ and Java source code.
